    <p><a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://aws.amazon.com/kinesis/data-streams/"
      }}>{`Amazon Kinesis Data Streams`}</a>{` is a scalable and durable real-time data streaming service that can continuously capture gigabytes of data per second from hundreds of thousands of sources. Making it an excellent candidate for streaming logs and metrics data.`}</p>
